Installation:

   -  git clone git://github.com/llnathanll/dotvim.git ~/.vim
   -  Create symlinks
   -  ln -s ~/dotvimfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
   -  ln -s ~/dotvimfiles/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
   -  cd ~/.vim
   -  git submodule update --init

Installing Vim Plugins:

    - cd dotvimfiles/plugins
    - clone plugin repository

Upgrading Vim Plugins:

    - cd ~/.vim/bundle/plugin_dir/
    - git pull origin master
    - or - 
    - git submodule foreach git pull origin master

Installing Colorschemes:
    
    install colorscheme to plugin directory
    create symlink in colors/ to plugins/colorscheme/colorscheme.vim
    
   
